&lt;p&gt;之前文章也写过，在家里使用晶晨S905L的电视盒子刷过OpenWrt系统，就是这篇文章：&lt;/p&gt;</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/soft-router-istoreos/featured.png"/></item><item><title>NAS数据迁移笔记</title><link>https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/nas-data-migration/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/nas-data-migration/</guid><description>&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;简述
